NK005(ca)012:0: dpal chen yang dag gi rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ru
NK005(ca)012:1: lu gsang ba'i dgongs pa bzhugs so na mo sh+r+ai
NK005(ca)012:3: dpal yang dag gi spros med rgyun gyi rnal 'byor la 'jug par 'dod pas /
NK005(ca)012:4: rdo rje slob dpon sogs skyabs sems tshogs bsags sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)012:5: thog mar mnyam nyid bde ba chen po byang chub
NK005(ca)012:6: sems kyi dbyings su mnyam par bzhag pas ting 'dzin
NK005(ca)012:7: rnam gsum dbyer med kyi tshul du /
NK005(ca)012:8: h'u phyi nang snod bcud chos nyid chen po ni
NK005(ca)012:9: rang bzhin rnam dag sems kyi spyod yul la sangs
NK005(ca)012:10: rgyas sems can gnyis su ngas ma mthong snang stong
NK005(ca)012:11: dbyer med rdo rje theg pa'i lam go ba'i yul
NK005(ca)012:12: 'di sangs rgyas bde chen zhing 'di nyid rnam dag
NK005(ca)012:13: sprul skur thug phrad gsal ru lu ru lu h'u
NK005(ca)012:14: b+h+yo h'u de nas phyi snod gzhal yas khang du
NK005(ca)012:15: gsal ba / h'u dbang chen yum lnga 'dus pa'i
NK005(ca)012:16: mkha' dbyings su srin po ma tram bsgral ba'i khog
NK005(ca)012:17: pa la ban+d+ha tshar gsum brtsegs pa'i rtsegs pa byas
NK005(ca)012:18: rak+ta'i spyin sbyar gnam lcags gzer chen btab yon tan
NK005(ca)012:19: che rgyas gru bzhi mchod rten tshul zla gam dbang
NK005(ca)012:20: chen smug nag 'bar ba na ka ba mchog brgyad
NK005(ca)012:21: ldan pa'i re cha dgu tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi mchog
NK005(ca)012:22: chen ka ba dang nyi zla'i ka zhu phag chen
NK005(ca)012:23: ka gdan dang sbrul gyi skyes bu ka ru'i ya
NK005(ca)012:24: spyib la rus sbal ma them zhing gi sgo 'geg
NK005(ca)012:25: ste ta la'i skyed shing 'dod yon lha mo dang
NK005(ca)012:26: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod gnas bcas te rab
NK005(ca)012:27: 'jigs dur khrod chen po'i rgyan dang chas mtha' dang
NK005(ca)012:28: dbus med ye shes nam mkha'i rgya dregs pa khyo
NK005(ca)012:29: shug bsnol zhing zhing chen bting rab gsal nyi ma'i
NK005(ca)012:30: gdan dang bcas pa 'di rgyu 'bras ma bkag dag
NK005(ca)012:31: pa'i gzhal yas khang dpal chen khrag 'thung tshogs kyi
NK005(ca)012:32: bzhugs gnas yin ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u
NK005(ca)012:34: h'u chos nyid skye med gdod nas dag pa la
NK005(ca)012:35: skye ba'i cho 'phrul 'bar ba'i skur bstan pa'i bcom
NK005(ca)012:36: ldan dpal chen khrag 'thung yab yum la ko sing
NK005(ca)012:37: la sogs mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ye shes skur
NK005(ca)012:38: gsal thugs rjes khyab pa'i sku gdug pa 'dul phyir
NK005(ca)012:39: 'jigs byed skur ston pa dur khrod rgyan mdzes gdug
NK005(ca)012:40: byed mtshon cha bsnams bskal pa'i me 'bar dur khrod
NK005(ca)012:41: dkyil 'khor na khams gsum stong mdzad khrag 'thung phyag
NK005(ca)012:42: rgya'i tshogs rgyu 'bras ma bkag lha yi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)012:43: gsal ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u de lta
NK005(ca)012:44: bu'i lha de gdod nas dam ye dbyer med kyi
NK005(ca)012:45: ngo bor nges pas dbang bskur byin rlabs spyan 'dren
NK005(ca)012:46: mi dgos la / mchod pa bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)012:47: h'u me tog bdug spos lha bshos mar me dang
NK005(ca)012:48: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' 'phan dang gdugs sil
NK005(ca)012:49: snyan rnga dung rin chen mu tig phreng gzugs sgra
NK005(ca)012:50: dri ro reg sogs lha mo'i tshogs bde chen byang
NK005(ca)012:51: chub sems kyi mchod sprin rnams dngos su bshams shing
NK005(ca)012:52: sems kyis rnam sprul te ye shes rang snang zhi
NK005(ca)012:54: mchod pa bzhes ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u
NK005(ca)012:56: h'u ni thabs chen shes rab sbyong ye shes thig
NK005(ca)012:57: le thugs la shar zur brgyad steng na 'bru brgyad
NK005(ca)012:58: 'phro khams gsum sems can sdug bsngal bsal rgyal ba
NK005(ca)012:59: rgya mtsho'i sku la thim sngags tshig sgra yi mchod
NK005(ca)012:60: pas mnyes tshur 'dus dang po'i gnas su thim lus
NK005(ca)012:61: ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs sku gsung thugs kyi
NK005(ca)012:62: dngos grub thob gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems
NK005(ca)012:63: 'bru brgyad yi ge 'phro zhing 'du ru lu ru
NK005(ca)012:64: lu h'u b+h+yo h'u zhes bzla zhing skabs su dzab
NK005(ca)012:66: dpal chen khrag 'thung thugs ni rin po che thugs
NK005(ca)012:67: rje sku mchog yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter bdag ni
NK005(ca)012:68: bla med byang chub mchog sems bskyed rang sems gdod
NK005(ca)012:69: nas ma skyes rin po che lha dang gnyis su
NK005(ca)012:70: med par mnyam bzhag nas ut+pala 'dab brgyad lta bu'i
NK005(ca)012:71: ljags brkyang zhing 'khur ba dbugs ring dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)012:72: yi ru lu ru lu 'khor lo tshogs chen po
NK005(ca)012:73: bar chad med pa'i bzlas brjod ting 'dzin gyis sems
NK005(ca)012:74: rtog sbyang zhing dngos grub stsal du gsol ru lu
NK005(ca)012:75: ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u gzhan yang spro na 'od
NK005(ca)012:76: zer dang lha la 'phro 'du btang ba dang ru
NK005(ca)012:77: lu phrin las su shes pa gzhung bzhin bya'o //
NK005(ca)012:78: bsnyen pa ji tsam nus pa dmigs pa gsal bas bzla zhing /
NK005(ca)012:79: rjes su bzlas brjod mchod par phul ba ni /
NK005(ca)012:80: sgrub pa po'i bzlas brjod kyi /
NK005(ca)012:81: ru lu thams cad bsdus te dpal chen po'i thugs kar phul la //
NK005(ca)012:82: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das bde bar gshegs
NK005(ca)012:83: so khro rgyal tshogs rgyal ba rgya mtsho 'khor bcas
NK005(ca)012:84: la bzlas brjod sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor mchod pa
NK005(ca)012:85: dam pa bla na med bzlas brjod mchod pa bzhes
NK005(ca)012:86: su gsol ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u de
NK005(ca)012:87: nas gong gi mchod pa bya /
NK005(ca)012:88: bshags pa ni ru lu bshags par shes pa'i skabs bzhin bya'o //
NK005(ca)012:89: de nas dngos grub bsdu ba /
NK005(ca)012:91: ye shes 'byam klas dkyil 'khor la bsgrub pa'i dkyil
NK005(ca)012:92: 'khor bsam mi khyab zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen
NK005(ca)012:93: dbang nub phyogs ngos su kha bltas te dus gsum
NK005(ca)012:94: sangs rgyas thams cad dang dpal chen khrag 'thung 'khor
NK005(ca)012:95: tshogs la tshon gang chos kyi 'khor lo las ru
NK005(ca)012:96: lu 'bru brgyad 'phro zhing 'du phar 'phros pas ni
NK005(ca)012:97: ye shes lha'i sku gsung thugs la mchod pa 'bul
NK005(ca)012:98: slar 'dus pas ni sgrub pa po'i sku gsung thugs
NK005(ca)012:99: kyi dngos grub thob ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo
NK005(ca)012:102: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa thugs rje khro
NK005(ca)012:103: dpal rngams pa'i tshogs 'bar pa'i byin rlabs rmad po
NK005(ca)012:104: che de nyid du ni bdag la stsol ru lu
NK005(ca)012:105: ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u zhes lha thams cad rang
NK005(ca)012:106: la thim pas dngos grub thob pas bsam /
NK005(ca)012:107: bsdu ldang bral ba'i don las bsdu ldang lhar ston pa ni /
NK005(ca)012:108: +aah phyag rgya'i cha lugs tha dad kyang dang por
NK005(ca)012:109: chos nyid ngang las byung bar du spyod pa ci
NK005(ca)012:110: spyad kyang kun bzang rol pa'i ngang du spyad tha
NK005(ca)012:111: mar rol pa'i snang ba yang chos nyid mnyam pa'i
NK005(ca)012:112: ngang du bsdu'o rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che
NK005(ca)012:113: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings rnam dag lam
NK005(ca)012:114: chen kun sgrol phyir mi skye mi 'gag cir mi
NK005(ca)012:115: dgongs ming dang mtshan ma ma grub pas mi gnas
NK005(ca)012:116: ma bral 'dus ma byas chos kyi dbyings kyis bsrungs
NK005(ca)012:117: pas na sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs so cis
NK005(ca)012:118: kyang mi phyed mi shigs pa'i stong pa'i go cha
NK005(ca)012:119: bla na med mtshan ma'i yul kun bcom nas kyang
NK005(ca)012:120: thams cad myur du rgyal bar gnas ru lu ru
NK005(ca)012:121: lu h'u b+h+yo h'u zhes pas go bgo ba byas
NK005(ca)012:122: nas dge bsngo bkra shis bya'o //
NK005(ca)012:123: 'di ni dpal yang dag he ru ka chen po'i
NK005(ca)012:124: spros med don gyi rnal 'byor grub brgya'i gshegs shul
NK005(ca)012:126: dpal he ru ka'i tan+t+ra las ru lu bye brag
NK005(ca)012:127: tu shes pa'i skabs nas lung gi tshul du rdo
NK005(ca)012:128: rje thugs mchog rtsal gyis btus pa mang+ga lam //
NK005(ca)012:129: 'di la dngos grub ji 'dod bzhin thob pa'i rten 'brel mchog yod do //
NK005(ca)012:130: rab tshes nyi ma lo'i zla ba brgyad pa'i tshes nyer brgyad la'o dge //
NK005(ca)012:131: yang dag rgyun khyer gyi tshogs bzhugs /
NK005(ca)012:132: mtshan ldan ban+d+ha stong gsum mnyam pa'i nang thabs shes
NK005(ca)012:133: dbyer med tshogs kyi longs spyad che 'dod yon lha
NK005(ca)012:134: mo'i sprin phung rab tu 'phro mnyam pa'i dam tshig
NK005(ca)012:135: bde chen rol bar gyur ram yam kham /
NK005(ca)012:136: +aahmh'u ho h'u dmigs med mkha' ltar dag cing khyab
NK005(ca)012:137: pa'i sku spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs
NK005(ca)012:138: kyang thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku'i rol pa las
NK005(ca)012:139: ye shes sgyu mar rol zhing gshegs su gsol e
NK005(ca)012:140: h+ye hi / badz+ra sa ma ya dza rdo rje
NK005(ca)012:141: sgeg mo rdo rje can rdo rje ma l+y+ae rin
NK005(ca)012:142: chen phreng rdo rje girti pad+ma'i dbyangs rdo rje nirti
NK005(ca)012:143: las kyi gar thabs dang shes rab tshogs ldan pa'i
NK005(ca)012:144: dkyil 'khor la yang dkyil 'khor rol sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa
NK005(ca)012:145: ga la s+y+aa h'u sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma l+y+aa
NK005(ca)012:146: tram sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga girti h+r+ai sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa
NK005(ca)012:147: ga nirti +aah bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam
NK005(ca)012:148: pa 'di ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par
NK005(ca)012:149: 'phro 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te
NK005(ca)012:150: dam tshig bzhin du ci bder bzhes su gsol sarba
NK005(ca)012:151: ga na tsakra p+au dza hoh dang po byang chub
NK005(ca)012:152: mchog tu sems bskyed nas rtsa ba yan lag bcas
NK005(ca)012:153: pa'i dam tshig las sems can dbang gis nor 'khrul
NK005(ca)012:154: ji mchis pa mi 'chab 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol
NK005(ca)012:156: e n+ri tri dza h'u bam ho pra be sha
NK005(ca)012:157: ya phata +aa be sha ya +aa khrag 'thung rdo
NK005(ca)012:158: rje 'khor bcas kyis 'jig rten khams ni rab 'byams
NK005(ca)012:159: na zhing gyur dag ni su yang rung ma lus
NK005(ca)012:160: bsdus te brlag par mdzod sarba dush+tana m+aa r+aa ya
NK005(ca)012:161: phata dbyings kyi zhal ni dug gsum rol pa'i hom
NK005(ca)012:162: 'bar ba'i klong du dug gsum bam gyi tshogs 'bul
NK005(ca)012:163: lo a la la ste bzhes nas kyang dngos grub
NK005(ca)012:164: bar chod bdud rnams med par gyis ma h+aa p+au
NK005(ca)012:165: dza kh+aa hi mnyam pa'i longs spyod bde ba che
NK005(ca)012:166: mtshan ldan sbyor bas thams cad 'grub lha tshogs kun
NK005(ca)012:167: kyang de bzhin du dgyes sbyor bde ba'i dngos grub
NK005(ca)012:168: thob ma h+aa su kha a la la ho dngos
NK005(ca)012:169: po chos nyid yangs pa'i klong du bskang snang ba
NK005(ca)012:170: ye shes chen po'i klong du bskang gsal ba shes
NK005(ca)012:171: rab 'bar ba'i klong du bskang sdug bsngal bde chen
NK005(ca)012:172: ka dag klong du bskang kun rdzob don dam gnyis
NK005(ca)012:173: su med par bskang mchod du med de gnyis med
NK005(ca)012:174: rol pas mchod bskang du med de skye med klong
NK005(ca)012:175: du bskang sbyor du med de zung 'jug chen por
NK005(ca)012:176: sbyor bsgral du med de mnyam nyid dbyings su sgrol
NK005(ca)012:177: ye sbyor ye sgrol chen po'i thugs dam bskang lhag
NK005(ca)012:179: khrag 'thung rol pa'i bka' nyan ni 'bar ma la
NK005(ca)012:180: sogs lhag sdud tshogs tshur gshegs dpal gyi pham phab
NK005(ca)012:181: bzhes dam skong phrin las 'grub par mdzod mi gnas
NK005(ca)012:182: ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du 'gyur ba med
NK005(ca)012:183: par lhun gyis grub pa dang rab 'byams rgyal ba'i
NK005(ca)012:184: bka' dbang thob nas ni 'gro ba yongs kyi dpal
NK005(ca)012:185: du 'gyur bar shog rnal 'byor kun tu bzang po
NK005(ca)012:186: rdo rje sems de dag ma skyes pa ni yum
NK005(ca)012:187: gyi mkha' yab yum dbye ba med pa'i sku gsung
NK005(ca)012:188: thugs 'bad rtsol med par lhun gyis grub par shog
NK005(ca)012:189: bkra shis gang zhig dngos grub 'byung ba'i gnas 'bar
NK005(ca)012:190: ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung rol pa'i sku mkha' 'gro
NK005(ca)012:191: mang po bde ba'i tshogs dang rol mchog tu mi
NK005(ca)012:192: 'gyur kun nas grub par shog grub pa'i 'bras bu
NK005(ca)012:193: mtha' yas kyi sems can don kun grub pa dang
NK005(ca)012:194: don grub bsam pa 'grub gyur pa'i bkra shis kun
NK005(ca)012:195: gyis bkra shig shog tshogs dang smon lam bkra shis
NK005(ca)012:196: dang bcas pa 'di ni cho ga snga ma'i kha
NK005(ca)012:197: skong du dpa' bo las rab gling pa la dag
NK005(ca)012:198: snang gi tshul du bka' babs pa'o //
NK005(ca)012:199: 'di yang rgyud kyi tshig sha stag yin par 'dug go //
NK005(ca)012:201: he ru ka'i ka lpo las /
NK005(ca)012:202: ru lu bshags par shes pa ni //
NK005(ca)012:203: ye shes lha tshogs zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor 'dir rig
NK005(ca)012:204: 'dzin dam can rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol tshe rabs
NK005(ca)012:205: thog mtha' med pa'i dus mtha' nas da lta lus
NK005(ca)012:206: 'di blangs pa yan chod du rang sems ma rig
NK005(ca)012:207: bdag tu bzung pa yis 'khor ba'i nyes skyon sna
NK005(ca)012:208: tshogs byung nas su kun gzhi'i blo la bag chags
NK005(ca)012:209: bsags pa dang bar du thugs rjes bzung dang stsol
NK005(ca)012:210: ba yis byang chub sems bskyed thar lam sgor zhugs
NK005(ca)012:211: te theg pa rim par bgrod cing spyad pa'i tshe
NK005(ca)012:212: tshul khrims sdom pa phyi nang dam tshig las zhig
NK005(ca)012:213: ral chag nyams gyur pa ji mchis dang khyad par
NK005(ca)012:214: gsang sngags theg pa'i sgor zhugs nas 'da' dka' sdom
NK005(ca)012:215: pa'i dam tshig mnos pa las sngon du spyod pa'i
NK005(ca)012:216: goms shugs chung ba yis nyams su ma rtogs gzhung
NK005(ca)012:217: bzhin ma spyad de bla ma mched la sri zhu
NK005(ca)012:218: brtse gdung chung sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun bcad gsang
NK005(ca)012:219: tshig spel mdzad spyod rnam lngas 'gro don lhur ma
NK005(ca)012:220: spang dug lnga rnam grol lam du gnas ma gyur
NK005(ca)012:221: mnyam pa'i mchod pas lta ba thag ma chod shes
NK005(ca)012:222: par bya ba'i spyad yul yal bar dor grub par
NK005(ca)012:223: bya ba'i 'bras bu rgyun thag bsring dbang dang mi
NK005(ca)012:224: ldan chos bshad las rnams brtsam rtogs pa stobs chung
NK005(ca)012:225: dag bsgom bsgrub la g.yeng dam rdzas mchod tshogs gzhung
NK005(ca)012:226: bzhin ma stob dang dam bcas khas blang bgyis kun
NK005(ca)012:227: rjes ma slob byang chub rigs can spyod pas thugs
NK005(ca)012:228: ma bsrung bar chad gnod skyen ma bzod 'khrul sems
NK005(ca)012:229: shor snod dang mi ldan grogs ngan grib mas phog
NK005(ca)012:230: de la sogs te nyes sdig ji bsags pa gnong
NK005(ca)012:231: 'gyod mthol bshags bzod par gsol lags na byams mgon
NK005(ca)012:232: thugs rjes tshangs par stsal du gsol ru lu ru
NK005(ca)012:233: lu h'u b+h+yo h'u bshags yul lha dang mkha' 'gro
NK005(ca)012:234: rig 'dzin pho nya'i tshogs la ru lu 'bru brgyad
NK005(ca)012:235: kyi ye shes 'od zer phar 'phros pas thams cad
NK005(ca)012:236: ye shes kyi 'od phung du gyur /
NK005(ca)012:237: bdag la tshur 'dus pas nyes skyon byang zhing dag
NK005(ca)012:238: nas ye shes kyi sku nag nog gi dri ma
NK005(ca)012:239: dang bral ba shel sgong phyis pa ltar gsal zhing
